          ul.list-unstyled.mb-4.pb-2
            li.d-block.pb-2.border-bottom <strong>Color:</strong> White
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>Dimensions:</strong> 100.6 x 46.3 x 45.1mm
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>Weight:</strong> 130 g
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>Camera:</strong> CMOS 8.4MP x2 / F2.2 lens (Default output pixel count - 15MP)
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>Video:</strong> 360˚ Dual Lens: up to 4096 x 2048 (24fps)
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>Battery:</strong> 1,160mAh
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>External Memory:</strong> MicroSD card (up to 256GB)
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>OS Convergence:</strong> Android, iOS - Mobile App / Windows, Mac - PC Software
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>Connectivity:</strong> Wi-Fi 802.11 (2.4/5GHz), Bluetooth v4.1, USB 2.0 (Type-C)
            li.d-block.py-2.border-bottom <strong>Sensor:</strong> Gyro, Accelerometer

